  <section class="page-section" aria-labelledby="section-improvathon">
    <h2 class="section-heading" id="section-improvathon">The Improvathon</h2>
    <div class="about-intro">
      <p class="about-where">Every so often we hand the venue over to improv for a full day, marathon included. We kick off with TheatreSports to set the tone, then run jams, intros, and signature formats back to back into the night. It is the easiest day to wander into and stay longer than you planned.</p>
